sentence.text: CYP450 Metabolized Drugs Results from in vitro and in vivo studies suggest that enfuvirtide is unlikely to have significant drug interactions with concomitantly administered drugs metabolized by CYP450 enzymes.
sentence.negationtags: <scope> CYP450 Metabolized Drugs Results from in vitro and in vivo studies suggest that enfuvirtide is <cue> unlikely </cue> </scope> to have significant drug interactions with concomitantly administered drugs metabolized by CYP450 enzymes.

sentence.text: Antiretroviral Agents: No drug interactions with other antiretroviral medications have been identified that would warrant alteration of either the enfuvirtide dose or the dose of the other antiretroviral medication.
